
run:
```
docker build -t flask-app .
docker run -p 5000:5000 -e DATABASE_URL="sqlite:///app.db" flask-app
```
Stop container:
``` docker stop flask-app ```
See active containers:
``` docker ps ```
Run deamon: 
``` docker run -d -p 5000:5000 --name flask-app flask-app ```
Stop Docker:
```
docker stop flask-app
docker rm flask-app
```

Create the database:
```
flask shell
>>> from app.extensions import db
>>> db.create_all()
```